    <item>
      <title>RSS fetch functions enhancement request</title>
      <link>http://projects.ez.no/rssfeed_operator/forum/general/rss_fetch_functions_enhancement_request</link>
      <description>Hi&#13;
&#13;
At first sight looks a bit similar to something I wrote for eZ Projects. I thought it was included in the enhancement request here: http://issues.ez.no/9933, but apparently it's not. I'll add a new patch there.&#13;
&#13;
Example code:&#13;
&lt;code&gt;&#13;
{def $rssList=fetch('rss','subtree_list',hash('node_id',$module_result.node_id, 'max_depth', $max_depth))}&#13;
{foreach $rssList as $rss}&#13;
&lt;link rel="alternate" type="application/rss+xml" title="{$rss.title|wash}" href={concat("/rss/feed/",$rss.access_url)|ezurl} /&gt;&#13;
{/foreach}&#13;
{undef $rssList}&#13;
&lt;/code&gt;</description>
      <author>community@ez.no (Administrator User)</author>
      <guid>http://projects.ez.no/rssfeed_operator/forum/general/rss_fetch_functions_enhancement_request</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 24 Jul 2008 09:09:12 +0000</pubDate>
